## ğŸ”§ Configuration Used

```python
CONFIG = {
    "starting_capital": 5000,
    "follow_percentage": 0.10,      # 10% of whale size
    "max_position_size": 500,       # $500 max per trade
    "min_whale_size": 25000,        # Only snipe whales > $25K
    "min_confidence": 70,           # 70% confidence threshold
    "stop_loss_pct": 15,            # -15% stop loss
    "take_profit_pct": 50,          # +50% take profit
    "max_daily_snipes": 20,         # 20 trades/day limit
    "slippage_pct": 0.5,            # 0.5% slippage assumption
}
```

